               <p>JOSHUA RAWLINSON. I am a <rs id="t18300708-44-viclabel248" type="occupation">clerk</rs>
                  <join result="persNameOccupation" targOrder="Y" targets="t18300708-44-victim366 t18300708-44-viclabel248"></join> in the City. On Sunday evening, the 13th of June, I was in the <placeName id="t18300708-44-crimeloc249">Edgware-road</placeName>
                  <interp inst="t18300708-44-crimeloc249" type="placeName" value="Edgware-road"></interp>
